      • initialize

        public void initialize​(java.net.URL location,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resources)
        Populates available parts table. Ensures that data can be written in the add products table. I was having a problem adding a product to the table. I could go in and type the information. However, on saving the product, nothing would be saved. I fixed this issue by adding this initialize method.
        Specified by:
        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
